;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:403px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					宫颈涂片：宮颈癌的发生率很高，宫颈刮片检查是筛检宮颈癌的有效方法，因此，凡有性行为之女性，每年应检查一次。</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:136px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					红外乳透<strong>（必须与外科联合组项）</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:40px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					　</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:40px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					　</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:40px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					●</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:403px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					用于检查乳腺增生和筛查乳腺肿物，具有安全、无创、快速的特点。乳腺疾病早期因症状不明显或肿物较小易被忽视，因此女性应每半年或一年做一次红外线乳透。</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td nowrap="nowrap" style="width:72px;height:33px;">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/spimg/images/file1351578230368.jpg" style="width: 680px; height: 53px;" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>全市通用！营业时间：上午7:30-10:30，浦东大道门诊部每周三休息，虹桥里门诊部每周二休息，广东路门诊部每周一休息</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/spimg/images/file1351578325402.jpg" style="width: 680px; height: 272px;" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/spimg/images/file1351578348473.jpg" style="width: 680px; height: 272px;" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/spimg/images/file1351578238705.jpg" style="width: 680px; height: 53px;" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	慈铭健康体检管理集团上海有限公司成立于2005年5月，目前拥有三家门诊部（分别位于人民广场、徐家汇、陆家嘴地区），是集健康体检、健康促进、健康管理为一体的专业医疗机构，近百名专业医护队伍，及GE、Siemens、Olympus等先进体检设备。</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	浦东大道门诊部</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	地址：浦东大道637号同科公寓2楼（浦东大道与东方路路口）电话：021-58793399</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;虹桥里门诊部</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	地址：徐汇区虹桥路188号元福大厦2楼，近徐家汇（虹桥路与宜山路路口）</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	电话：021-64691919</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;广东路门诊部</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	地址：黄浦区广东路429号天赐公寓2楼，近人民广场（广东路与福建中路路口）</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	电话：021-53263399</p>\r\n', 10);
